    "type": "message",
    "text": "Cool! I like this idea a lot. One way to frame is almost like a Steve-Blank-style get-out-of-the-building customer interview. I’d be curious to ask programmers about the emotions they feel about different languages they like and don’t like, and about how they’d describe their biggest frustrations with programming\n\nHowever I think who you interview is the most important question. I’d be more interested in customer interviews with non-programmers or beginner programmers than with expert programmers, but that’s a matter of taste I guess",
